title: Picnic Time Cabernet Wine Tool Set 889-00-179-000-0 - Overview
description:
Picnic Time Cabernet Wine Tool Set - 889-00-179-000-0 http://www.abt.com/product/92344/Picnic-Time-889001790000.html

The Cabernet is an eight-piece box set of wine accessories that is a welcome addition to anyones wine bar. It includes 1 lever-style cork-pull 2 bottle stoppers 1 drip ring 1 foil cutter 1 pourer/stopper 1 wine thermometer and 1 extra cork-pull. The box measures 8-11/16 x 7-3/16 x 4-7/8 and is made of black premium leatherette with white accent stitching. The Cabernet makes a thoughtful gift for your wine-loving friends.
